# =================================================================
# 👑 THE ULTIMATE .claudignore TEMPLATE (上帝级 AI 屏蔽清单)
# 核心目的：省 Token、降噪音、防幻觉、护隐私
# =================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. 🛑 绝对 Token 杀手 (巨大且全是机器生成的代码，AI读了必疯)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml
poetry.lock
Cargo.lock
Gemfile.lock
composer.lock
mix.lock

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. 🔐 敏感信息与密钥 (防暴雷，绝对不能喂给 AI)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.cert
*.crt
*.p12
*.jks
credentials.json
secret_token.rb
id_rsa
id_rsa.pub

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. 📦 前端与 Node.js 巨兽
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.next/
.nuxt/
.output/
.vuepress/dist
.serverless/
coverage/
.npm/
.yarn/
*.min.js
*.min.css
*.map

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. 🐍 Python 杂质
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
venv/
.venv/
env/
.env_dir/
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt
.tox/
.coverage
.coverage.*
nosetests.xml
coverage.xml
*.cover
*.log
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.hypothesis/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 5. ☕ Java / JVM 编译产物
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
target/
*.class
*.jar
*.war
*.nar
*.ear
*.log
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.rar
.gradle/
build/
!gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar
.m2/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 6. 🐹 Go, Rust, C/C++ 等编译型语言
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
bin/
pkg/
vendor/
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.o
*.obj
*.out
*.a
*.lib

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 7. 📊 庞大的数据文件 (上下文克星)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
*.sql
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.dump
*.csv
*.tsv
*.parquet
*.jsonl
*.xlsx
*.pdf
*.md5

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 8. 🖼️ 媒体与静态资源 (AI 看不懂二进制文本)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.ico
*.webp
*.mp4
*.mp3
*.wav
*.flac
*.ogg
*.ttf
*.woff
*.woff2
*.eot

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 9. 💻 操作系统与 IDE 垃圾 (纯噪音)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.csproj

# -----------------------------------------------------------------
# 10. 📝 杂项与日志
# -----------------------------------------------------------------
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*
tmp/
temp/